QuestData.Title: Champion Armaments
QuestData.Description:
See Lurr? He big and strong, but not so smart, not like Murr. Murr can make Lurr build good things for you, things for your Champions to wear and be smashier.
First, you give Murr something?
QuestData.LogDescription: Place a work order for Champion armaments and equipment.

Objectives.Objective: Place a work order for Champion armaments
